Cunningham, Respondent, v. Fitzgerald, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. April 13, 1892.) -Action by John T. Cunningham against John M. Fitzgerald.

Argued before Dwight, P. J., and Macomber and Lewis, JJ.

Nfo opinion. Motion for a reargument denied. See 17 N. Y. Supp. 341.
